The '''Sarlacc Project''', also known as '''Project Sarlacc''', was an attempt by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] to create a [[Super Star Destroyer prototype]] shortly after the [[Battle of Utapau/Legends|end]] of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It was foiled by an [[Alderaanian Resistance|early rebel cell]] from [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] during the [[Battle of Byss]].

However, Sarlac Project would later result in the construction of the [[Executor-class Star Dreadnought/Legends|''Executor''-class Star Dreadnought]] [[Executor/Legends|''Executor'']].<ref name="TEA">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref>

